-- IEEE 754 regression inputs that are not present in Intel readtest.in.
-- No-exponent overflow rows where pinned Intel BID C ignores rnd_mode (always
-- returns Inf); this repository follows IEEE 754 directed-rounding overflow
-- semantics, so native C comparison is skipped for these rows.
-- Divergence verified by direct probe of the pinned Intel C library.

